# LoL Build Coach — Complete High Level Design
**Version:** 1.0  |  **Date:** March 2026  |  **Author:** B

---

## 1. Overview

LoL Build Coach is a locally installed Windows application that provides real-time,
AI-powered item build recommendations for League of Legends. It reads live game state
from the official Riot Live Client Data API, enriches it with current meta data and
per-champion custom resources (YouTube guides, articles, PDFs), then queries an
AI provider of the user's choice to generate contextual build advice.

The UI is served as a local web application accessible at http://127.0.0.1:8765
in the user's browser — no cloud backend, no hosting costs, no data leaving the
machine except for AI API calls.

