## 5. Security Model

  Layer                  Mechanism                        Protects Against
  ─────────────────────  ───────────────────────────────  ─────────────────────────────
  Network binding        host=127.0.0.1 (never 0.0.0.0)  Remote network access
  CORS policy            Allow-Origin: 127.0.0.1:8765     Cross-origin browser requests
  Session token          32-byte URL-safe, file mode 600  Unauthenticated API calls
  Token comparison       hmac.compare_digest (SHA-256)    Timing oracle attacks
  Timestamp validation   ±30s window on /api/ask          Replay attacks
  API key storage        keyring (+ file fallback)        Plaintext key exposure
  Input validation       Pydantic extra=forbid + regex    Parameter pollution / injection
  Rate limiting          slowapi 10/min ask, 5/min ingest Runaway AI API spend
  Security headers       CSP, X-Frame-Options, nosniff    XSS, clickjacking, MIME
  Logging policy         access_log=False, no key values  Token/key leakage in logs
  OpenAPI disabled       docs_url=None, openapi_url=None  Schema reconnaissance
  Vanguard safety        No injection, no overlay window  Anti-cheat detection

