## 6. API Reference

  Method   Path                     Auth    Rate Limit   Description
  ───────  ───────────────────────  ──────  ───────────  ──────────────────────────
  GET      /bootstrap               None    —            Deliver session token to SPA
  WS       /ws?token=<t>            Token   —            Live game state stream
  POST     /api/ask                 Token   10/min       Build recommendation
  GET      /api/resources           Token   60/min       List resources (filter: ?champion=)
  POST     /api/resources           Token   5/min        Ingest new resource
