  GET      /api/settings            Token   60/min       Get provider (no raw key returned)
  POST     /api/settings            Token   60/min       Set provider + save key to keyring
  GET      /api/meta/status         Token   60/min       Last meta refresh time + patch
  POST     /api/meta/refresh        Token   2/hour       Manually trigger meta refresh
  GET      /                        None    —            React SPA (static)

