## 7. Data Models

  GameState
  ├── activePlayer: { summonerName, championName, level, currentGold }
  ├── allies:       [ PlayerSlim x5 ]
  ├── enemies:      [ PlayerSlim x5 ]  ← primary input for build logic
  ├── gameTime:     float (seconds)
  └── gameMode:     str

  PlayerSlim
  ├── summonerName, championName, team, position, isDead
  └── items: [ { id: int, name: str } x6 ]

  AskRequest
  ├── question:   str (max 500)
  ├── champion:   str (max 32)
  ├── role:       TOP | JUNGLE | MID | BOT | SUPPORT
  ├── gameState:  GameState | None
  └── timestamp:  ISO8601 (replay protection)

  AddResourceRequest
  ├── champion:   str (alphanumeric, lowercased)
  ├── url:        HttpUrl
  ├── label:      str (max 120)
  └── type:       youtube | article | pdf | note

  BuildResponse
  ├── items:      [ { name, cost, reason } x6 ]
  ├── runes:      { keystone, secondary, shards }
  ├── skillOrder: str
  └── rationale:  str (plain English, cites source if from custom resource)

