## 9. Tech Stack

  Layer              Technology                  Reason
  ─────────────────  ──────────────────────────  ─────────────────────────────────
  Backend            FastAPI + Uvicorn            Async, fast, serves API + static
  Real-time          WebSocket (FastAPI native)   Push game state without polling
  AI routing         LangChain                   Provider-agnostic LLM interface
  Embeddings         text-embedding-3-large       Best retrieval quality (OpenAI)
  Vector store       ChromaDB PersistentClient    Embedded, no server, per-champion
  Database           SQLite via SQLModel           Zero-config, local, typed ORM
  Meta scraping      httpx + BeautifulSoup         Lightweight, no Selenium needed
  Transcript ingest  youtube-transcript-api        Official captions, no yt-dlp
  Scheduling         APScheduler                  In-process cron, no Celery needed
  Credential store   keyring (+ file fallback)    OS-protected, never plaintext
  Rate limiting      slowapi                      FastAPI-native, minimal config
  Frontend           React + Vite + shadcn/ui     Modern, dark mode, zero overhead
  State mgmt         TanStack Query               Server-state caching + WS sync
  Tray               pystray + Pillow             Lightweight, no Qt dependency
  Bundling           PyInstaller --onefile        Single portable .exe, no install

