## 10. Build & Release (Portable)

  Step  Command / Action
  ────  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  1     cd frontend && npm install && npm run build
        → outputs frontend/dist/ (served by FastAPI as static files)

  2     pip install -r requirements.txt
        pyinstaller --onefile --noconsole --name lolcoach tray.py
        → outputs dist/lolcoach.exe (~120MB bundled)

  3     Distribute lolcoach.exe — user drops it anywhere and runs it.
        No installer, no service, no registry changes.

  4     On first launch:
          - data/ folder created next to lolcoach.exe
          - .token generated (mode 600)
          - SQLite DB initialised in data/lolcoach.db
          - ChromaDB persisted in data/chroma/
          - Browser opens to http://127.0.0.1:8765/?autoAuth=1

